Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりました｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:45.13,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.66,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,"The northern winds are what made the Vikings," right?
