Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:57.75,Main,Will Zeppeli,0,0,0,,Simply put, overcoming hardship is an opportunity for growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち 厳しい条件は➡
